participants.url: In a relationship with Ben Super

messages.message: I didn't mean to be disrespectful or anything, I just miss my friend, we've been friends for years. I have a boyfriend as well. Chase and I haven't ever dated we've just been good friends.

Brian
Does your husband have friends that post pictures with their tits out that miss him
?
I hope not.
I don't mean to be disrespectful.

I think you are incredibly disrespectful when I haven't done anything to you. You were the one who thought of it as sexual, I honestly just tried to find a photo of us after work. It might have been thoughtless, and when you said that I took the photo down in case she did find it disrespectful because I love Chase and want his relationship to work out. I just missed my friend, I do not like him in that way and I don't have a husband because he physically and emotionally amused me and cheated on me. I wouldn't ever want to hurt someone the way I was hurt.
